	.ptm {
	  
	    max-width: 1180px !important;
		padding-left: 0.9375rem;
		padding-right: 0.9375rem;
		margin: 0 auto;
		
		    padding-top: 10px;
			@media only screen and (max-width: 1024px) {
				padding-left: 20px;
				padding-right: 20px;
			}
	}
	.ptm:before, .ptm:after {
	  content: " ";
	  display: table;
	}
	.ptm:after {
	  clear: both;
	}

	.ptm .col-quarter, .ptm .col-half, .ptm .col-one-fourth {
	  position: relative;
	  min-height: 1px;
	  
	  
	}

	@media (min-width: 34em) {
		.ptm .col-quarter {
			float: left;
			width: 75%;
		}
		.ptm .col-half {
			float: left;
			width: 49%;
		}
		.ptm .col-one-fourth {
			float: left;
			width: 25%;
		}
	}
	

	.ptm .wrapper-fixed {
		
	}
	.ptm .wrapper-fliud {
		
	}
	@media only screen and (max-width: 640px) {
      .ptm .leg {
        
      }
    }
	.ptm .wrapper-fixed .leg {
		float: left;
		margin-right: 10px;
		padding: 5px 10px;
		/* border: 1px solid #bfbfbf; */
		-moz-border-radius: 3px;
		-webkit-border-radius: 3px;
		border-radius: 3px;
		background-color: transparent;
	}
	.Bongo-ui .ptm .wrapper-fixed .leg {
		background-color: #f2f2f2;
	}
	.ptm .pax-detailed {
		padding: 12px 10px;
		-moz-border-radius: 3px;
		  -webkit-border-radius: 3px;
		  border-radius: 3px;
	}
	
	.ptm .ib {
		display: inline-block;
		vertical-align: top;
	}
	.ptm .text-left {
		text-align: left;
	}
	.ptm .fs-xs {
		font-size: 0.7857rem;
	}
	.ptm .fs-md {
		font-size: 0.91rem !important;
	}
	.ptm .fs-sm {
		font-size: 0.6571rem;
	}
	.ptm .block {
		display: block;
	}
	.ptm .bold {
		font-family: "Lato Bold";
		font-weight: normal;
	}
	.ptm .gray-dark {
		color: #333;
	}
	.ptm p {
		margin-top: -2px;
	}
	.ptm .text-xs-center {
	  text-align: center;
	}
	@media (min-width: 34em) {
	  .ptm .text-sm-right {
		text-align: right;
	  }
	}
	
	<!-- new pax styles -->
	.ptm .pax-names {
		
	}
	.ptm .main-list {
		padding: 0;
		margin: 0;
		list-style-type: none;
	}
	.ptm .main-list li{
		display: inline-block;
		vertical-align: top;
		position: relative;
		padding: 0px 5px;
		font-size: 14px;
		text-transform: capitalize;
	}
	.ptm .main-list li:after {
		border-left: 1px solid #B7B7B7;
		content: "";
		position: absolute;
		top: 6px;
		left: 0;
		height: 10px;
    }
	.ptm .main-list li:first-child:after {
		border-left: 0;
	}
	
	.ptm .sub-list {
